<h3>Translations</h3>
The Bika dictionaries are ready for translation via the easy-to-use web interface at <a class="external-link" href="https://www.transifex.net/projects/p/bika-lims/resource/bika/">Transifex.net</a>. Please see <a class="external-link" href="http://www.bikalabs.com/helpcentre/how-to/transifex">How to translate Gaob Bika 3
</a><br /><br />
<p>Approved new translations will be taken up into future Bika releases but can also be downloaded directly from Transifex<br /><br />The Transifex interface provides a fun way to translate Bika - do so for your language now!</p>
</td>
